            . I am an officer. On the 10th of April I was in Brick-lane, <placeName id="t18320517-138-crimeloc812">Spitalfields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320517-138-crimeloc812" type="placeName" value="Spitalfields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320517-138-crimeloc812" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320517-138-off810 t18320517-138-crimeloc812"></join> - I saw the prisoner coming along with another young man, with a great coat under his arm - I had not got many yards further before I met an old gentleman, who said he had stolen a great coat out of a cart; I turned after the prisoner, the other person who was with him ran off - I followed the prisoner down to Black Eagle-street, where I saw him with the coat on, and he tried to throw it off; I had seen him put it on.</p>
